# EchoChain Lifecycle Analytics

## Objective

Analyze second-hand marketplace data to understand product lifecycle, resale trends, pricing behavior, and circular economy insights.

## Goals

- Collect product data
- Clean datasets
- Analyze resale trends
- Build dashboard
- Generate business insights

## Technologies

- Python
- Scrapy
- Pandas
- PySpark
- Databricks
- Power BI
- Git
